query:
SELECT mj.id, mj.trackId, mj.status, mj.platform, mj.platformJobId, mj.completedAt,
       t.title as track_title, a.id as album_id, a.title as album_title,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM audioFiles af WHERE af.trackId = mj.trackId) as audio_file_count
FROM musicJobs mj
JOIN tracks t ON t.id = mj.trackId
JOIN albums a ON a.id = t.albumId
WHERE mj.status = 'completed'
HAVING audio_file_count = 0
LIMIT 20;
